{"id":151661,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/人生只有900个月/","date":"2011-05-11T05:17:08Z","modified":"2011-05-11T05:17:08Z","title":"人生只有900个月","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>最令你吃惊的事实是什么？——人生只有900个月。事实上，你可以画一个30×30的表格，一张A4纸就够了。每过一个月，就在一个格子里打钩。你全部的人生就在这张纸上。你会因此有一个清晰的概念：你的人生是如何蹉跎的。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/64dac98cjw1dh2h7umaejj.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\"><b>编辑推荐</b></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\">\n                    <a title=\"人生总结\" href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2009%2F11%2F602.html&#038;from=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2011%2F05%2F27700.html\"><br />\n                        <img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/site_images/2011/04/23/6271512.jpg\" width=\"96px\" height=\"96px\" /><br />\n                        人生总结<br />\n                    </a>\n                </td>\n<td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\">\n                    <a title=\"人生的位置\" href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2009%2F11%2F593.html&#038;from=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2011%2F05%2F27700.html\"><br />\n                        <img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/site_images/2011/04/23/6268687.jpg\" width=\"96px\" height=\"96px\" /><br />\n                        人生的位置<br />\n                    </a>\n                </td>\n<td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\">\n                    <a title=\"植物大战僵尸人里的人生哲理\" href=\"http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect.htm?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2010%2F08%2F6926.html&#038;from=http%3A%2F%2Fzazazi.com%2F2011%2F05%2F27700.html\"><br />\n                        <img src=\"http://static.wumii.com/site_images/2011/04/23/6310349.jpg\" width=\"96px\" height=\"96px\" /><br />\n                        植物大战僵尸人里的人生哲理<br />\n                    </a>\n                </td>\n<td width=\"102\" valign=\"top\">\n                    <a title=\"人生就像北京地铁1号线\" h